  "description": "<p><strong>感谢<a href=\"http://www.phonele.com\" target=\"_blank\">蜂乐网</a>的投递</strong><br /></p><p>今天@安卓论坛 在腾讯微博上爆出了小米3工程机正面照。 小米3采用5.5寸1080P全高清屏幕、骁龙800处理器、3GB RAM、16GB+32GB ROM、500W前置+1300W后置摄像头、3600MAH电池、将会支持NFC、米Hifi、搭载miui V5，在8月16日小米会推出多个电子产品，同时手机不止只有一款，米粉们觉得这个怎么样，怎么看着眼熟？</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e709f5b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244129.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B33%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244129.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B33%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244129.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B33%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244129.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B33%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%B7%E6%9C%BA%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2%E7%85%A7%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244129.htm&amp;t=%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B33%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A0%B