  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/244127.htm", 
  "description": "<p>OLPC是一家旨在为孩子们提供廉价的笔记本和平板电脑的高科技公司，尤其是那些在世界上不算太富裕的地区。正如该公司的名字所寓意的，它们的使命就是——为每个孩子提供一台笔记本。<strong>从本质上来说，OLPC XO就是一台廉价的Android平板电脑，只是为了面向孩童教学而定制了用户界面。OLPC XO平板原本应该在上个月到来的，但是跳票到了这个月。</strong><br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e709f59/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244127.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%B3%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%9AOLPC+XO%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E7%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%B4%A7%E6%B2%83%E5%B0%94%E7%8E%9B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244127.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%B3%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%9AOLPC+XO%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E7%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%B4%A7%E6%B2%83%E5%B0%94%E7%8E%9B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244127.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%B3%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%9AOLPC+XO%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E7%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%B4%A7%E6%B2%83%E5%B0%94%E7%8E%9B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244127.htm&amp;t=%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%B3%E7%A5%A8%EF%BC%9AOLPC+XO%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B3%E6%9D%BF%E5%B0%86%E4%BA%8E7%E6%9C%8816%E6%97%A5%E5%88%B0%E8%B4%A7%E6%B2%83%E5%B0%94%E7%8E%9B\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share